For example updating djoser to latest version when using django 1.7 updates django as well to latest version. It's because of `install_requires` in `setup.py` which is set to value of `requirements.txt` file. `install_requires` should be empty like e.g. in Django Rest Framework itself.

I believe that fix of this issue should update readme file too.

